com.arctro.cachemap

Class PassiveCacheMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arctro.cachemap.PassiveCacheMap<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - The key type
    V - The value type

    public class PassiveCacheMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    A hashmap that stores values and expire times for the values. Unlike a CacheMap it does not check if a value has expired until a function has been called on it. It then checks if the value has expired and removes it if needed.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ben McLean
